{"tid":734902,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴西球迷掟石觀歡迎國家隊回國","createTime":"2018-07-09T05:05:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T17:39:45.000Z","uid":55981,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7febfdd32b8a36500e6fbf2f2c8d09f00035b5b6","tid":734902,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:05:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://beta.ems.ladbiblegroup.com/s3/content/808x455/1e6623615b42982f1c607eb1cc9946b5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbeta.ems.ladbiblegroup.com%2Fs3%2Fcontent%2F808x455%2F1e6623615b42982f1c607eb1cc9946b5.png&h=1a7dcfb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴西國家隊於俄羅斯世界盃8強以1:2不敵比利時出局後，周日已經返抵巴西，大批忠實球迷在里約熱內盧國際機場後迎接巴西隊並向他們歡呼。然而當球隊乘坐隊巴離開時，卻有憤怒的球迷向隊巴投擲石頭及雞蛋以宣洩不滿。<br />\n<br />\n巴西隊現身機場時，不少球迷在場迎接，亦有球迷要求與菲臘比古天奴及教練迪堤等合照，迪堤及後簡短地表示，衷心感謝球迷的熱情。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HpotJcCKxqA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHpotJcCKxqA&d=EpBiDWHeHEVQSoaZVRr9hUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=e26f3675\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HpotJcCKxqA</a>"},{"pid":"e7a988b3db0b360b610d4cede35865932622e8d2","tid":734902,"uid":51828,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:11:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ebb08b3cfa52e61696f321e5a10a6f04e493939","tid":734902,"uid":132587,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:16:20.000Z","msg":"尼馬係車入面訓低左未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37dbfacd9bf482950bf27ac39126ab14d2d630f1","tid":734902,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:17:38.000Z","msg":"抵! <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5293ac6def330ee7dd9ff69cc86feacb3a770db8","tid":734902,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:18:58.000Z","